## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-213"><xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowBlock.Encapsulate%2A>方法需要兩個現有的區塊： 目標區塊 (實作類別的執行個體<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601>) 和來源區塊 (實作類別的執行個體<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601>)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-213">The <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowBlock.Encapsulate%2A> method requires two existing blocks: a target block (an instance of a class that implements <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601>) and a source block (an instance of a class that implements <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601>).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-214"><xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowBlock.Encapsulate%2A> 建立連接的內部類別的新執行個體<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601>介面成員`target`參數和<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601>介面成員`source`參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-214"><xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowBlock.Encapsulate%2A> creates a new instance of an internal class that connects the <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601> interface members to the `target` parameter and the <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601> interface members to the `source` parameter.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-215">同時<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601>和<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601>衍生自<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.IDataflowBlock>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-215">Both <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601> and <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601> derive from <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.IDataflowBlock>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-216">從來源到目標明確傳遞區塊的完成。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-216">Block completion is explicitly passed from sources to targets.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-217">因此，<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.IDataflowBlock.Complete%2A>和<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.IDataflowBlock.Fault%2A>方法連線到目標，同時<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.IDataflowBlock.Completion%2A>屬性連接到來源。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-217">Therefore, the <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.IDataflowBlock.Complete%2A> and <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.IDataflowBlock.Fault%2A> methods are connected to the target while the <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.IDataflowBlock.Completion%2A> property is connected to the source.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-218">您必須確定當一半完成時，目標一半取得完成以最適當的方式; 的來源例如：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-218">You must ensure that when the target half  completes, the source half gets completed in the most appropriate manner; for example:</span></span>  
  
 `target.Completion.ContinueWith(completion => source.Complete());`  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-219">或者，如果您想要散佈完成類型，您可以使用這個更複雜的程式碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-219">Or, if you want to propagate the completion type, you can use this more sophisticated code:</span></span>  
  
```  
target.Completion.ContinueWith(completion => { if (completion.IsFaulted) 3   
  
((IDataflowBlock)batchBlock).Fault(completion.Exception);   
else   
batchBlock.Complete();   
});  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-220">您必須同時也可以明確提供訊息傳播從目標到來源。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-220">You must also explicitly provide the message propagation from target to source.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-221">這個明確連線的好處是，它能讓您自由地執行兩個封裝區塊之間任何未受限制的處理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-221">The benefit of this explicit connection is that it gives you the freedom to perform any unconstrained processing between the two encapsulated blocks.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-222">您可以執行，編碼成區塊的委派 （如果這些區塊會取得委派） 所需的處理，或內嵌區塊之間的子網路。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-222">You may do that either by encoding the necessary processing into the blocks' delegates (if the blocks take delegates), or by embedding a sub-network of blocks between them.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c3e6d-223">更簡單的方法是使用區塊採用委派。例如，使用<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ActionBlock%601>， <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.TransformBlock%602>， <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.TransformManyBlock%602> （如果適用），或自訂的區塊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3e6d-223">The easier way is to use a block that takes delegates; for example, use <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ActionBlock%601>, <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.TransformBlock%602>, <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.TransformManyBlock%602> (if applicable), or a custom block.</span></span>

